=== 使用 ===
* This template inserts the new [[Russian ruble]] sign {{Russian ruble}}. 

A wikilink can be added optionally:
* <code><nowiki>{{Russian ruble}}</nowiki></code> &rarr; {{Russian ruble}}
* <code><nowiki>{{Russian ruble|link=currency symbol}}</nowiki></code> &rarr; {{Russian ruble|link=currency symbol}}
* <code><nowiki>{{Russian ruble|oldsign=yes}}</nowiki></code> &rarr; {{Russian ruble|oldsign=yes}}
* <code><nowiki>{{Russian ruble|link=currency symbol|oldsign=yes}}</nowiki></code> &rarr; {{Russian ruble|link=currency symbol|oldsign=yes}}
* <code><nowiki>{{Russian ruble|link=Russian ruble}}</nowiki></code> &rarr; {{Russian ruble|link=Russian ruble}}

<!-- this doesn't work with the current implementation because of the link= parameter
The [[WP:ALT|alt text]] is "RUB". Use <code>|alt=</code> to use something different.
-->

Do not use this template in the "title" parameter of a citation template. It will result in an error and will not display correctly.

Note that if <code>oldsign=yes</code> is set this template uses [[:File:Rouble official sign for small display.svg|Rouble official sign for small display.svg]], a serif version of the ruble sign tweaked to render legibly at small point sizes. Otherwise it uses [[:File:Ruble sign.svg|Ruble sign.svg]], the official sans-serif version of the symbol.

